description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/29855/documentation

This is a linking activity which links the product  hydrocarbons, aromatic, cyclic (C9+) to the generic market for residual hydrocarbon mix, from steam cracking operations. All chemicals that enter this market provide the function of a fuels.

The activity starts with the reception of raw materials at the factory gate.

The activity ends with the production of residual hydrocarbon mix, from steam cracking operations for the generic market.
